{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Newspapers are dying for a few reasons."},{"time":3000,"text":"Readers don't want to pay for yesterday's news, and advertisers follow them."},{"time":7000,"text":"Your iPhone, your laptop,"},{"time":9000,"text":"is much more handy than New York Times on Sunday."},{"time":12000,"text":"And we should save trees in the end."},{"time":15000,"text":"So it's enough to bury any industry."},{"time":18000,"text":"So, should we rather ask, \"Can anything save newspapers?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":22000,"text":"There are several scenarios for the future newspaper."},{"time":24000,"text":"Some people say it should be free;"},{"time":27000,"text":"it should be tabloid, or even smaller: A4;"},{"time":30000,"text":"it should be local, run by communities,"},{"time":33000,"text":"or niche, for some smaller groups like business --"},{"time":35000,"text":"but then it's not free; it's very expensive."},{"time":38000,"text":"It should be opinion-driven;"},{"time":40000,"text":"less news, more views."},{"time":43000,"text":"And we'd rather read it during breakfast,"},{"time":45000,"text":"because later we listen to radio in a car,"},{"time":48000,"text":"check your mail at work and in the evening you watch TV."},{"time":51000,"text":"Sounds nice, but this can only buy time."},{"time":54000,"text":"Because in the long run,"},{"time":56000,"text":"I think there is no reason, no practical reason"},{"time":58000,"text":"for newspapers to survive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61000,"text":"So what can we do?"},{"time":63000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":64000,"text":"Let me tell you my story."},{"time":66000,"text":"20 years ago, Bonnier, Swedish publisher,"},{"time":69000,"text":"started to set newspapers in the former Soviet Bloc."},{"time":73000,"text":"After a few years, they had several newspapers in central and eastern Europe."},{"time":76000,"text":"They were run by an inexperienced staff,"},{"time":79000,"text":"with no visual culture, no budgets for visuals --"},{"time":84000,"text":"in many places there were not even art directors."},{"time":86000,"text":"I decided to be -- to work for them as an art director."},{"time":90000,"text":"Before, I was an architect, and my grandmother asked me once,"},{"time":93000,"text":"\"What are you doing for a living?\""},{"time":95000,"text":"I said, \"I'm designing newspapers.\""},{"time":97000,"text":"\"What? There's nothing to design there. It's just boring letters\""},{"time":100000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":101000,"text":"And she was right. I was very frustrated, until one day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105000,"text":"I came to London, and I've seen performance by Cirque du Soleil."},{"time":109000,"text":"And I had a revelation. I thought,"},{"time":111000,"text":"\"These guys took some creepy,"},{"time":113000,"text":"run-down entertainment,"},{"time":115000,"text":"and put it to the highest possible level of performance art.\""},{"time":119000,"text":"I thought \"Oh my God, maybe I can do the same with these boring newspapers.\""},{"time":122000,"text":"And I did. We started to redesign them, one by one."},{"time":126000,"text":"The front page became our signature."},{"time":129000,"text":"It was my personal intimate channel to talk to the readers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133000,"text":"I'm not going to tell you stories about teamwork or cooperation."},{"time":137000,"text":"My approach was very egotistic."},{"time":139000,"text":"I wanted my artistic statement,"},{"time":142000,"text":"my interpretation of reality."},{"time":144000,"text":"I wanted to make posters, not newspapers."},{"time":146000,"text":"Not even magazines: posters."},{"time":148000,"text":"We were experimenting with type,"},{"time":151000,"text":"with illustration, with photos. And we had fun."},{"time":154000,"text":"Soon it started to bring results."},{"time":157000,"text":"In Poland, our pages were named"},{"time":161000,"text":"\"Covers of the Year\" three times in a row."},{"time":165000,"text":"Other examples you can see here are from"},{"time":167000,"text":"Latvia, Lithuania, Estonia --"},{"time":169000,"text":"the central European countries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173000,"text":"But it's not only about the front page."},{"time":176000,"text":"The secret is that we were treating"},{"time":178000,"text":"the whole newspaper as one piece,"},{"time":180000,"text":"as one composition -- like music."},{"time":184000,"text":"And music has a rhythm, has ups and downs."},{"time":188000,"text":"And design is responsible for this experience."},{"time":192000,"text":"Flipping through pages is readers experience,"},{"time":194000,"text":"and I'm responsible for this experience."},{"time":197000,"text":"We treated two pages, both spreads, as a one page,"},{"time":200000,"text":"because that's how readers perceive it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203000,"text":"You can see some Russian pages here which got many awards"},{"time":205000,"text":"on biggest infographic competition in Spain."},{"time":209000,"text":"But the real award came from Society for Newspaper Design."},{"time":214000,"text":"Just a year after redesigning this newspaper in Poland,"},{"time":217000,"text":"they name it the World's Best-Designed Newspaper."},{"time":219000,"text":"And two years later,"},{"time":221000,"text":"the same award came to Estonia."},{"time":224000,"text":"Isn't amazing?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":227000,"text":"What really makes it amazing: that the circulation of these newspapers"},{"time":229000,"text":"were growing too."},{"time":231000,"text":"Just some examples:"},{"time":233000,"text":"in Russia, plus 11 after one year,"},{"time":235000,"text":"plus 29 after three years of the redesign."},{"time":238000,"text":"Same in Poland: plus 13, up to 35 percent"},{"time":241000,"text":"raise of circulation after three years."},{"time":244000,"text":"You can see on a graph,"},{"time":246000,"text":"after years of stagnation, the paper started to grow,"},{"time":249000,"text":"just after redesign."},{"time":252000,"text":"But the real hit was in Bulgaria."},{"time":254000,"text":"And that is really amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258000,"text":"Did design do this?"},{"time":260000,"text":"Design was just a part of the process."},{"time":262000,"text":"And the process we made was not about changing the look,"},{"time":264000,"text":"it was about improving the product completely."},{"time":268000,"text":"I took an architectural rule about function and form"},{"time":271000,"text":"and translated it into newspaper content and design."},{"time":274000,"text":"And I put strategy at the top of it."},{"time":276000,"text":"So first you ask a big question: why we do it? What is the goal?"},{"time":279000,"text":"Then we adjust the content accordingly."},{"time":281000,"text":"And then, usually after two months, we start designing."},{"time":284000,"text":"My bosses, in the beginning, were very surprised."},{"time":286000,"text":"Why am I asking all of these business questions,"},{"time":288000,"text":"instead of just showing them pages?"},{"time":290000,"text":"But soon they realized that this is the new role of designer:"},{"time":292000,"text":"to be in this process from the very beginning to the very end."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295000,"text":"So what is the lesson behind it?"},{"time":297000,"text":"The first lesson is about that design can change not just your product."},{"time":301000,"text":"It can change your workflow -- actually, it can change everything in your company;"},{"time":305000,"text":"it can turn your company upside down."},{"time":307000,"text":"It can even change you."},{"time":309000,"text":"And who's responsible? Designers."},{"time":312000,"text":"Give power to designers."},{"time":314000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":318000,"text":"But the second is even more important."},{"time":321000,"text":"You can live in a small poor country, like me."},{"time":324000,"text":"You can work for a small company,"},{"time":327000,"text":"in a boring branch."},{"time":329000,"text":"You can have no budgets, no people --"},{"time":331000,"text":"but still can put your work to the highest possible level."},{"time":335000,"text":"And everybody can do it."},{"time":337000,"text":"You just need inspiration, vision and determination."},{"time":341000,"text":"And you need to remember that to be good"},{"time":343000,"text":"is not enough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345000,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}